<item>
            <title>[FELIX-1766] Refactor and enable AdminServiceMBean</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-1766</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The MBean for the AdminService is currently not registered with the MBean Server. &lt;br/&gt;
Before it can be registered it needs to be refactored to be more coarse-grained, like the FeaturesServiceMBean.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
